{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/VariantBuilderProtocol"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/VariantBuilderProtocol\/end()","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Ends the builder process and returns the constructed value."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/variantbuilderprotocol\/end()"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:4GLib22VariantBuilderProtocolPAAE3endAA0B3RefVSgyF","extendedModule":"GLib","roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"end()","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"end","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV","text":"VariantRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"modules":[{"name":"GLib"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"end"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/VariantRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV","text":"VariantRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is not permissible to use ","type":"text"},{"code":"builder","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" in any way after this call"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"except for reference counting operations (in the case of a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"heap-allocated "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/VariantBuilder","isActive":true},{"text":") or